   <userestrict>
            <head>Restrictions on access:</head>
            <p>The materials in this collection are open to only current members and alumnae of Pi
               Beta Phi Sorority, NY Delta Chapter. Pi Beta Phi provides and updates list of active
               members. Photo ID is also required. All others require permission from the NY Delta
               Chapter President and the Vice President of Fraternity Development, either in person,
               by signed letter, or email.</p>
